			if = { 
				limit = {

						which = hxr
						value = 1
					}
					OR = { 
						NOT = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = hxy
								value = 1
							}
						}
						NOT = { 
							is_variable_equal = { 
								which = hxn
								which = hxt
							}

					NOT = {

							which = arh
							which = hxt
						}
					}

				if = { 
					limit = { 
						ai = no
					}
					hidden_effect = { 
						change_variable = { 
							which = ahf
							value = -300
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ahf
									value = 1200
								}
							}

								limit = { 
									stability = 3
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = ahf
									value = 1200
								}

							else = { 
								subtract_variable = { 
									which = ahf
									value = 1200
								}
								add_stability = 1
							}

								NOT = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = ahf
										value = 0
									}
								}
							}
							if = { 
								limit = { 
									NOT = {

									}
								}
								set_variable = {

									value = 0
								}
							}
							else = { 
								change_variable = { 
									which = ahf
									value = 1200
								}
								add_stability = -1
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ahd
							which = ahf
						}
						divide_variable = { 
							which = ahd
							value = 12
						}
						multiply_variable = { 
							which = ahd
							value = 0.1
						}
						multiply_variable = { 
							which = ahd
							value = 10
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = lsc
							value = 100
						}
						subtract_variable = { 
							which = lsc
							which = ahd
						}
					}
					custom_tooltip = POP_StabSubtract25
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							is_emperor_of_china = yes
						}
						add_mandate = -1
					}
				}
			}
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				check_variable = {

					value = 1
				}
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					ai = no
				}

									which = ahf
									value = 0
								}
							}

							limit = { 
								NOT = {

								}
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = ahf
								value = 0
							}
						}
						else = { 
							change_variable = {

								value = 1200
							}

					}
					set_variable = {

					}
					divide_variable = { 
						which = ahd
						value = 12
					}
					multiply_variable = { 
						which = ahd
						value = 0.1
					}
					multiply_variable = { 
						which = ahd
						value = 10
					}

						value = 100
					}

						which = ahd
					}

					limit = {

					}
					add_mandate = -1
				}
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = hxr
				value = 0
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = hxs
				value = 0
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = hxt
				value = 0
			}

		else = {

		else = { 
			set_variable = { 
				which = hro
				value = 0
			}
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				AND = { 
					OR = { 
						custom_trigger_tooltip = { 
							tooltip = is_monarchy_tt
							OR = { 
								government = monarchy

								value = 0

					}
				}
				has_heir = no
			}
			clr_country_flag = Had_Heir
		}
		else = { 
			set_country_flag = Had_Heir
		}
		trigger_switch = { 
			on_trigger = total_development
			2000 = { 
				if = { 
					limit = {

							government_rank = 6

					set_government_rank = 5

			}
			400 = {

					limit = { 
						OR = { 
							NOT = { 
								government_rank = 4
							}
							government_rank = 5
						}
					}
					set_government_rank = 4
				}
			}
			100 = { 
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						OR = { 
							NOT = { 
								government_rank = 3
							}
							government_rank = 4
						}
					}
					set_government_rank = 3
				}
			}
			30 = { 
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						OR = { 
							NOT = { 
								government_rank = 2
							}
							government_rank = 3
						}
					}
					set_government_rank = 2
				}
			}
			1 = { 
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						government_rank = 2
					}
					set_government_rank = 1
				}
			}
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				ai = yes
				AND = { 
					num_of_cities = 1
					NOT = { 
						tag = AAA
					}
				}
			}

				which = osf

			}
			change_variable = {

			divide_variable = {
